        <h2>Badges</h2>
        
        <p>Badges help members be sure who you are and what you can do! The more you collect, the more Job Posters and Taskers will trust in your abilities.
        </p>
        <p> Badges are issued when specific requirements are met. A green tick shows that the verification is currently active. </p>

        <h6>ID Badges</h6>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6 badge-box">
            <div class="badege-icon">
              <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
            </div>
             <div class="badged-description">
              <div class="description"><label>Police Check</label><p>Provide peace of mind to other members by successfully completing a Police Check</p></div>
              <div class="actions">
                <a href="<%= site_url("account/badge/police-verification")%>" class="btn-sm btn btn--primary">Add</a>
              </div>
             </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-sm-6 badge-box">
            <div class="badege-icon">
              <i class="icon icon-Mastercard"></i>
            </div>
             <div class="badged-description">
              <div class="description"><label>Digital iD</label><p>Give members a reason to choose you - knowing that your identity is verified with Australia Post’s Digital iD.</p></div>
              <div class="actions">
                <a href="#" class="btn-sm btn btn--primary">Add</a>
              </div>
             </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-sm-6 badge-box">
            <div class="badege-icon">
              <i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i>
            </div>
             <div class="badged-description">
              <div class="description"><label>Payment Method</label><p>Make payments with ease by having your payment method verified.</p></div>
              <div class="actions">
             
              <% if (paymentverify) { %>
                 <span>verified</span>
              <% } else { %>
                 <a href="<%= site_url("account/payment-methods") %>" class="btn-sm btn btn--primary">Add</a>
              <% } %>
              
               
              </div>
             </div>
          </div>


           <div class="col-sm-6 badge-box">
            <div class="badege-icon">
              <i class="fa fa-mobile"></i>
            </div>
             <div class="badged-description">
              <div class="description"><label>Mobile</label><p>Verified when you join, you'll receive instant task notifications and can make free calls via Airtasker.</p></div>
              <div class="actions">

               <% if(bagdedata.mobile_verify==1) { %>
                 <span>verified</span>
               <% } else { %>
                 <a href="<%= site_url("account/mobile-settings") %>" class="btn-sm btn btn--primary">Add</a>
               <% } %>
              
               
                
              </div>
             </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-sm-6 badge-box">
